Req_Content_Snippet:
Let's have a validation shema for time field. Create a time  shema in common and add something like this
stringRequired.test({
    message: { key: 'time.invalid' },
    test: (value) => {
      if (!value) {
        return true;
      }

      const parsedDate = parse(value, TIME_FORMAT, new Date());

      return isValid(parsedDate);
    },
  })
And add Invalid time  label to errors.json 
Allow user to type text but show the correct validation message.
Address this comment as well:

